<B><FONT SIZE=6><P ALIGN="CENTER">MPEG-1</P>
<HR>
<P ALIGN="CENTER">&nbsp;</P>

<UL>
</FONT><FONT SIZE=6><LI>First standard developed by the group (1992)</LI>
<LI>A standard for the coding of a combined audio-visual signal at a bitrate around 1.5 Mbit/s</LI>
<LI>Work motivated by the concept of videos on CDs with a VHS cassette type of quality</LI>
<LI>Video Compression ratios between 8:1 and 30:1</LI></UL>

